item.title: Beef Nilaga
item.description: Slow cooked beef stew with vegetables INGREDIENTS 1 kilo beef shank (leg portion) 3-4 medium potatoes 1 piece chinese cabbage (wombok) 1⁄4 kg. green breens (bitsuelas) 1 large onion 1 cup chopped celery stalk 1⁄2 tbsp. black pepper corns 3-4 tbsp. patis to taste spring onions for garnish
